<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f3f4f6;">
  <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #f3f4f6;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
        <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
          <tr>
            <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316 0%, #ea580c 100%); padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;">
              <h1 style="margin: 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700;">⚠️ No-Show Recorded</h1>
              <p style="margin: 8px 0 0; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-size: 14px;">Your Scheduled Adoption Pickup</p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px 30px;">
              <h2 style="margin: 0 0 20px; color: #1f2937; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600;">
                Missed Adoption Appointment
              </h2>
              <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
                We noticed that you did not arrive for your scheduled adoption pickup of <strong style="color: #f97316;"><%= @pet&.name %></strong> on <strong><%= @adoption_date.strftime('%A, %B %-d, %Y') %></strong>.
              </p>

              <!-- Pet Details Card -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #fff7ed; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #f97316; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 20px;">
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 12px; color: #1f2937; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600;"><%= @pet&.name %></p>
                    <p style="margin: 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;">
                      <%= @pet&.pet_type&.capitalize %><% if @pet&.breed.present? %> • <%= @pet.breed %><% end %><% if @pet&.age.present? %> • <%= @pet.age %> years<% end %>
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Important Notice -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #fff7ed; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #f97316; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 20px;">
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 12px; color: #92400e; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">📝 What Happens Next?</p>
                    <p style="margin: 0; color: #92400e; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8;">
                      You have the opportunity to reschedule your adoption. However, you're only allowed up to <strong>2 reschedules</strong>. If you miss another appointment after that, your adoption request will be automatically rejected.
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Action Information Card -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #eff6ff; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #0284c7; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 20px;">
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 12px; color: #0c4a6e; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">🔄 Option to Reschedule</p>
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 12px; color: #0c4a6e; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">
                      Our admin team will be in touch shortly with options to reschedule your adoption. Please contact us if you have any questions or if you'd like to reschedule right away.
                    </p>
                    <p style="margin: 0; color: #0c4a6e; font-size: 13px;">
                      If you're unable to proceed with the adoption at this time, please let us know so we can make <%= @pet&.name %> available to other loving families.
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Contact Information -->
              <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #f3f4f6; border-radius: 6px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 0;">
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">📞 Contact Us</p>
                    <p style="margin: 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;">
                      Pet Haven Hub, Panauti, Kathmandu, Nepal<br>
                      We're here to help!
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="margin: 0; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;">
                Thank you for your interest in adopting from Pet Haven Hub.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
